Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是在這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.33,0:01:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的會出現嗎?傳說中的海盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出…出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海盜！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.42,0:02:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向右轉舵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.99,0:02:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十五話\N真紅之海賊\N被拆散的劍心與小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海盜   海龍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有船被襲擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.18,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是\N從昨天開始就什麼也沒吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想吃饅魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸蝦也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是伊勢的龍蝦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.06,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來\N也很久沒吃牛肉火鍋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家  來吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.21,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近聽說有點困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會只有這些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這些而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三人給我分來吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出去教課了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要吃中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼   你把我當什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小…生只要頭就可以了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下   頭是要丟掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你尾巴就可以了\N只是吃飯的資格而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼\N小鬼吃盤子忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…還有剩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒有了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是啊薰害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是誰害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寄住在這裏的有兩人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只來吃飯的有一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那麼辛苦的出去教課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是非常努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在賺取生活費嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們三個男人只會聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊晃來晃去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃女人的還能這麼悠閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還能在天下行走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼伊勢龍蝦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒賺一文錢還敢在那邊說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要去那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有衣服沒洗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙說得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生也許對小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了也不一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是忽然要我們去賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們除了劍術很厲害之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有什麼可取之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有本事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在馬上到千本屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請到千本屋來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.83,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不會讓你們覺得失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.17,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能乘船的給40元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有本事的人能賺100元或200元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,100！200元？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們千本屋連續4條船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被海盜襲擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天船還要出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.16,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何我們想要保住船隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.30,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以當保鏢來乘船者就給40元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能取得海盜的首級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會付相當的賞金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,40元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2~3個月可以輕鬆的過活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這樣做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐船就是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海盜嗎   已經很久沒打架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.70,0:06:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊   跟著大家就乘上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有10天的旅行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經寫信拜託別人\N交給大小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.71,0:07:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊   這樣就可以買伊勢龍蝦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家給阿薰了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經開始暈船了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~賺錢真是一件\N不簡單的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小   小薰小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍   劍心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇   不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…？那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.96,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為\N想讓你們吃好吃的東西所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才在這船裏工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要出去教課根本是在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N說了的話你們會擔心的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心   你的手沒在動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小薰小姐  太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍再怎麼說也說海盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.42,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起   那句話還不足以形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍是惡鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙從空中襲來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把行李都搶光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵抗的人全部被殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是叫朱羅的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對   是朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見朱羅的人都沒活著回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖被說成是沒血沒淚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是誰也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的真正的身份\N是謎樣的怪物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的千本屋是做絹布為生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他只以我的船為目標呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何拜託各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請保護這條船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可能還不太習慣坐船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡不著覺   劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不   我是因為在想些\N讓我有點在意的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是朱羅這怪物的事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.74,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來海上的戰鬥\N小生就已經不如海盜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在我知道小薰小姐\N也在這船上後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管發生什麼事我都會阻止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向你保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不會增加你的麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有劍心的保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭了   暴風雨要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對   特別是這條船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁夜晚來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼樣傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來像閃電一樣快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅   那就是朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一位要先犧牲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你砍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無名小卒根本不是他的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我成為你的對手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在為止所做的是不對的\N海盜先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人了嗎\N能再認真跟我戰鬥的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐   快到船內去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在這裏的話就太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會對你綁手綁腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥   保護小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險   劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快…快點藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏到裏 面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.29,0:14:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋   不要粗手粗腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好   無論如何\N這貨物一定要保住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使其他的貨物被搶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.04,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要剩下這個就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.87,0:14:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你致富的貨物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋伍兵衛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不   應該是伍兵衛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.15,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是哪一個都一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.93,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本是\N沒有被殺價值的蒼蠅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是體貼的男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是外國的香煙嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐有沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成這樣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是\N不要離開小生的身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人   先把那女人捉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是那傢伙的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要緊的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男的讓我朱羅來殺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在為止\N沒有一個男人能勝過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎樣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好強…一次都沒抽中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的男人是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報上名來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村…劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心，打倒你後\N這世界就只有我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸…輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心劍心振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要緊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會中了毒鏢之後還跟我打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該…該不會是海軍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…只是一艘警備艇而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貨物都搶完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了   撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正只是恐嚇而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙沒有來這裏的膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看上她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要…放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小…小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅   拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把小薰小姐放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把沒有任何罪過的人捉走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你開什麼玩笑混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要殺女人及小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們海盜的規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是值得誇耀的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是殺女人的卑鄙漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎？相反的你必需要留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.29,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在為止沒有一個人\N是我朱羅的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你\N我要用我的手來解決你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的命賣給死神了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那女的放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐   不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅老大   快把船開走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.73,0:20:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個男人\N故意不給我最後的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處死刑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處死刑！！處死刑！\N處死刑！！
