Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.91,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥！左之助！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.15,0:21:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰小姐拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…劍心

